Popular IT parks in Hitech City, Mindspace Madhapur IT Park and Gachibowli are within 7 km from the locale
Proximity to IT Hubs generates demand for rental accommodation to the locale
Vittal Rao Nagar Road, Hitech Avenue Road, and Durgam Cheruvu Road connect the locale to other parts of the city
Just 2 km from Vikas Industrial Park, whereas Kukatpally & Mini Industrial Estate (Hafeezpet) are within 12 km radius
Only 6 km from Borabanda Railway Station located on Multi-Modal Transport System & Secunderabad-Falaknuma line
Rajiv Gandhi International Airport is about 35 km away via Nehru Outer Ring Road
Amgre Mall, InOrbit Mall, Mana Mall, and IKEA are within 4 km from the locality
Vivero Int. Pre School, Narayana Co School Madhapur, & KLAY PreSchool & Daycare are situated in the locale

Shilparamam, an arts and crafts village, is situated just 3 km away via Hitech City Main Road
Vittal Rao Nagar residents complain about sewage overflow on public roads
